OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FThe Secretary of State for Northern
OL,7,FIreland has said the disorder in
OL,8,FBelfast "has to stop".
OL,10,FFollowing the second night of disorder
OL,11,Fin the city, Hilary Benn called the
OL,12,Fscenes "truly shocking" and said it
OL,13,Fwas not representative of "the vast
OL,14,Fmajority of people in Northern
OL,15,FIreland".
OL,17,FPolice and rioters clashed for a
OL,18,Fsecond night on Wednesday over the
OL,19,FBelfast knife attack, which saw 16
OL,20,Farrests made and 12 officers injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
