OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781208361
OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FPolice officers were pelted with
OL,7,Fbricks and petrol bombs and used water
OL,8,Fcannons on the balaclava-clad rioters
OL,9,Fin Co Antrim, on the outskirts of
OL,10,FBelfast.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News, Benn called for
OL,13,Fcalm saying the riots are "doing
OL,14,Fimmense damage and harm".
OL,16,FBenn said "people have been terrified"
OL,17,Fand described scenes where people have
OL,18,Fbeen stopped in their cars and asked
OL,19,Ffor their nationality.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
