OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781208361
OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FDescribing the arson attacks, he said:
OL,7,F"Imagine masked thugs coming to your
OL,8,Fdoor in the middle of the night
OL,9,Ftelling you to get out and trying to
OL,10,Fset fire to your house".
OL,12,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary said
OL,13,Fthat these acts were "completely
OL,14,Funacceptable" and that the police
OL,15,F"will be coming" for anyone engaging
OL,16,Fin violence.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
