OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781208361
OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FBenn went on to pay tribute to the
OL,7,Femergency services for their bravery
OL,8,Fin walking "towards that danger to
OL,9,Fprotect people".
OL,11,FHe also thanked the communities across
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland who "offered shelter
OL,13,Fand support" to those displaced
OL,14,Fbecause of the violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
