OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FThe protests have been forcing further
OL,7,Fscrutiny on the government's migration
OL,8,Fplan, which Benn defended saying that
OL,9,F"net migration is down" and said that
OL,10,Fsince 2024 the government have
OL,11,F"deported nearly 70,000 people and
OL,12,Fnearly 1,000 in Northern Ireland
OL,13,Falone".
OL,15,FThe Secretary of State confirmed he
OL,16,Fhad been in contact with the Irish
OL,17,Fgovernment and the Northern Ireland
OL,18,FExecutive, with a particular focus on
OL,19,Fthe protection of the Common Travel
OL,20,FArea (CTA).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
