OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FIrish Justice Minister Jim O'Callaghan
OL,7,Fconfirmed that "significant Border
OL,8,FManagement Unit doorstop operations
OL,9,Fnow take place at Dublin Airport" and
OL,10,Fthat the number of people arriving
OL,11,Fwithout documentation has reduced
OL,12,Fsince 2023.
OL,14,FShadow Defence Secretary, James
OL,15,FCartlidge called for the government to
OL,16,F"get a grip" on the disorder in
OL,17,FBelfast and said that "people want to
OL,18,Fsee action".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
