PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781208361
OL,3,CBelfast disorder 'has to stop' says
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland Secretary
OL,6,FCartlidge called the unrest "a danger
OL,7,Fto society" and said it was
OL,8,F"unacceptable".
OL,10,FThe sister of murdered MP Jo Cox urged
OL,11,Fpeople not to "create chaos" as she
OL,12,Fcondemned the racist and violent
OL,13,Fscenes in Northern Ireland.
OL,15,FKim Leadbeater said she understands
OL,16,Fanger at Monday's knife attack but
OL,17,Fappealed for people not to "riot and
OL,18,Fcause more trouble and more problems".
